n: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14pt;\">、自由发言与讨论（11:00-11:30）</span></strong></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 29.2pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20pt;\">欢迎各届朋友报名参加！</span></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; line-height: 20pt; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14pt;\">报名请提前发“姓名、单位、职务、手机、邮箱”等信息至会务组。联系人：张寒&nbsp;15802758029，zhangh@ige-live.com。</span></div><p><br/></p>', '2', '10000', '', '0', '1', '');
INSERT INTO `jbr_article_data` VALUES ('128', '<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">各有关单位和非职务发明专利权人：</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">2016</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">年度第二批武汉市知识产权奖励资助政策兑现工作已经启动，现将有关事宜通知如下：</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星黑体\">一、专利资助类</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星楷体\">（一）中国发明专利授权与集成电路布图设计专有权登记资助（含香港、澳门、台湾地区）</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">、政策标准</span></strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">发明专利:以第一专利权人为准，单位为5000元/件，个人为1500元/件。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;