s New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">、资助时段</span></strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">2016</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">年9月1日--12月31日</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">、资助对象及申报条件</span></strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">（1）第一专利权人登记注册和纳税地均在本市行政区域范围内的企业，上年度纳税额超过10万元，且向国家知识产权局或外国专利局提交专利申请文件时所留通信地址在本市行政区域范围内。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">（2）第一专利权人需同时是第一申请人，并由第一专利权人缴纳该专利的相关费用。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 文星仿宋\">（3）申请资助的专利已请求国务院专利行政部门进行保密审查，或者向国务院专利行政部门提交专利国际申请。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, &#39;serif&#39;; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">