om: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第二条&nbsp;&nbsp;专家库集成科技、产业和经济高层次人才，服务于国家科技管理，是国家科技管理信息系统的重要组成部分。按照共建共享的目标，积极鼓励引导专家为地方和社会各方发展提供服务。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第三条&nbsp;&nbsp;专家库按照广泛参加、统一建设、科学管理、规范使用、有序开发的原则建设和运行。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第四条&nbsp;&nbsp;国家科技行政管理部门牵头专家库建设的总体部署和统筹协调，研究制定相关政策和管理制度。委托部内相关单位分工负责，开展专家库建设、运行维护、开发利用等相关工作。</span></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></h1><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第二章&nbsp;专家信息资源建设</strong></span></h1><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第五条&nbsp;&nbsp;专家库由科技界、产业界和经济界的高层次专家组成。原则上应符合以下基本条件：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（一）科技界专家主要是从事科技研发、科技创新政策研究或项目管理，或在主要国际学术组织中任中高级职务、具有较高专业水平的专家。原则上应具有副高级及以上职称，或作为负责人承担过中央财政支持的国家科技计划项目（课题），或是国家科技奖励获得者。研究成果突出的优秀青年学者可适当放宽条件。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（二）产业界专家主要是科技型上市公司、国家高新技术企业、国家创新型（试点）企业、国家级高新区、科技园区和各类创业服务机构、行业协会学会的高级管理人员等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（三）经济界专家主要是熟悉国家科技经费审计的注册会计师，或高等学校、科研院所、企业等的财务审计部门负责人，知识产权法、民商法等相关领域高水平专家；知名创业服务机构的创业导师，天使投资或创业投资机构的高级管理人员，资本市场、银行信贷及保险等机构中高级管理人员等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第六条&nbsp;&nbsp;专家进入专家库有两种方式。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（一）每年新增的中国科学院院士、中国工程院院士、海外高层次人才引进计划（千人计划）和国家高层次人才特殊支持计划（万人计划）自然科学与工程领域入选者、长江学者、中央财政科技计划（专项、基金等）项目负责人、国家科技奖励获奖人等，经本人同意可直接入库。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（二）其他符合条件的专家可由本人申请、经单位推荐和科技人才管理与服务单位信息校验后入库。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第七条&nbsp;&nbsp;专家库积极吸纳海外专家，采取专业机构邀请、专家自愿申报、国内专家联名推荐等多种形式增加库内海外专家数量。海外专家原则上应当在本领域知名高等学校、科研院所和企业任职，或在国际科技组织担任高级职务，或获得本领域国际大奖，在学术界较为活跃。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第八条&nbsp;&nbsp;专家所在单位负责本单位的专家推荐、信息审核和重大事项报告工作，及时按照部署要求，组织专家登陆国家科技管理信息系统对本人信息进行定期核对、补充。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第三章&nbsp;专家库管理与维护</strong></span></h1><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第九条&nbsp;专家库每年组织一次专家信息集中更新。系统通过短信、邮件等方式通知在库专家，登陆网上系统，确认专家单位、职务、联系方式等关键信息变更情况，并对系统所提供的最新获奖、论文及承担国家课题等情况进行核实确认。各单位审核后录入系统。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第十条&nbsp;&nbsp;入库专家可随时在线更新本人信息。专家库系统将积极拓展信息更新渠道，采取多种方式采集和补充专家信息，扩大专家库规模，并对新入库和更新的专家信息进行审核校验。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第十一条&nbsp;专家连续两年未对个人信息进行更新确认，系统将进入冻结状态，并通知专家本人。专家重新登陆并确认信息后，可解除冻结状态。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第十二条&nbsp;有以下或其他不适宜参加评审活动的情况，专家所在单位应及时报告，相关专家自动退出专家库：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（一）违法违纪；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（二）开除公职或党籍；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（三）学术失范。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">因身体原因或其他原因，专家本人可申请退出专家库。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第四章&nbsp;专家选取及使用</strong></span></h1><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第十三条&nbsp;&nbsp;中央财政科技计划（项目、基金等）各管理部门、直属机构主管司局和专业机构等因项目评审评估、结题验收、评价奖励等管理活动所需专家，一律从专家库中选取。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">各地方科技行政管理部门、各行业、各地方专业机构需要使用专家库专家的，按照专家抽取与使用的管理规定和专家自愿参与的原则，依申请使用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第十四条&nbsp;&nbsp;专家使用坚持轮换原则。原则上每位专家每年参与评审项目不超过10次，避免同一专家反复多次参加各类评审活动，保障专家科研时间。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第十五条&nbsp;&nbsp;从专家库中抽取项目评审咨询专家，一般应遵循随机原则。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（一）专家使用单位明确提出专家选取条件、专家组结构、回避要求及抽取方式，在线提交后，由系统随机产生候选专家。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（二）专家库通过语义分析、数据挖掘、机器学习等大数据技术和人工智能方法，开展专家活跃度评价、影响力评价和小同行标识匹配，支撑服务专家抽取工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">（三）专家使用单位认为候选专家不能完全满足评审需求的，可采取特邀方式选取部分建议专家，并需按要求向社会公开，接受监督。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第十六条&nbsp;专家选取遵循回避原则。符合以下条件的专家不能参加项目评审，包括：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">1.&nbsp;被评审项目的负责人或参与人员。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">2.&nbsp;与被评审项目负责人或任务（课题）负责人5年之内有共同承担项目、申报奖励、发表论文、申请专利等合作关系；与被评审项目申报负责人或任务（课题）负责人有近亲属关系、师生关系（硕士、博士期间）以及其他重大利益关系。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;24个月内与被评审项目申报单位及任务（课题）牵头单位有过聘用关系，包括现任该单位的咨询或顾问。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">4.&nbsp;所在单位与被评审项目申报单位及任务（课题）牵头单位有行政隶属关系。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">5.&nbsp;与被评审项目申报单位及任务（课题）牵头单位有经济利害关系，如持有涉及申报单位的股权（申报单位为上市公司的除外）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">6.&nbsp;被评审项目评审前声明提出的回避事项，如存在利益竞争或学术争议的单位及个人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">7.&nbsp;其他有可能妨碍评审公正性的情形。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">专家使用单位可根据实际工作需求，提出更详细明确的回避条件。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第十七条 专家库建立评价机制。通过使用单位评价、专家相互评价及被评审项目评价等多种方式对专家参与评审咨询活动情况进行记录，作为后续专家使用参考。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第五章&nbsp;专家服务</strong></span></h1><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第十八条 专家库采取多种形式，向在库专家推送国家科技战略规划制定、科技前沿信息、科技计划管理、科技政策等信息，积极创造条件，促进专家学术交流与合作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第十九条 专家库广泛吸纳各界人才入库，组织动员在库人才助力科研活动和成果转化及大众创业万众创新，服务行业和地方发展，服务国家创新驱动发展全局。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第六章&nbsp;监督评估与罚则</strong></span></h1><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">第二十条 &nbsp;除涉密及法律法规另有规定外，项目评审专家名单应当向社会公开，接受社会监督。对采用视频或会议方式评审的，公布专家名单，强化专家自律，接受同行质询和社会监督；对采用通讯方式评审的，评审前专家名单严格保密，评审后向社会公开，保证评审公正性。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br ', '2', '10000', '', '0', '1', '');
INSERT INTO `jbr_article_data` VALUES ('144', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">反腐大剧《人民的名义》一经播出，便引发全民观剧热潮。但此剧播出不到30集时，全部55集的“送审样片”却被提前泄露上网，疑似遭遇盗版侵权。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《人民的名义》总监制、总发行人李学政表示，“送审样片”遭遇泄露，背后的内幕一定比《人民的名义》还要精彩。学者分析认为，剧集泄露行为或给权利人带来重大影响和损失，侵犯了权利人的著作人身权和财产权，可考虑刑事制裁。 &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《人民的名义》，可谓带有“自热”体质，一走上荧屏，就迎来了“全民追剧”。且不说这样一部现象片，有着强大的影响力，单看看制作单位，来头这么大，竟然还遭遇泄露上网，这从一个侧面表明了当前知识产权保护的不尽如人意。 &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一切其来有自，《人民的名义》遭遇泄露，不是偶然的。当前中国对于知识产权的重视已经达到了前所未有的高度，其中一个证明是，“仅在2015年，国务院下发的 国办 、 国发 文件中，就有27件提及知识产权。”但是，当前依然存在着知识产权保护的严峻挑战。有资料表明，仅在2014年一年内，全国各级法院新收知识产权民事一审案件95522件，同比增长7.83%；新收知识产权行政一审案件9918件，同比增长243.7%。还有大量的侵权行为，隐藏在水平面下。 &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">今年4月26日，我们将迎来第17个世界知识产权日，主题是“创新改变生活”。“苟日新，日日新，又日新”，还从来没有一种力量像创新这样，深刻地改变着我们的生产生活。特别是随着互联网的到来，我们深刻感受到了创新的力量。知识产权是创新的必要前提，没有创新，世界将停滞不前；没有知识产权，创新将会成为无源之水。正是在这样的背景下，《人民的名义》遭遇泄露，是那么的“辣眼睛”。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">面对《人民的名义》的非法传播，湖南卫视等该片制作方称已经报案。由于该剧的强大影响力，想来这几天不法分子应该会惶惶不可终日，甚至有可能采取一些“去痕”手段。这里考验的是道高还是魔高。有关方面肯定会高度重视，最终呈现出“魔高一尺，道高一丈”，正义压倒邪恶，让不法分子付出应有的代价。 &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">需要指出的是，即便《人民的名义》得到了正义的匡扶，也并不代表当前知识产权保护就完美无缺。就实际来看，中国的知识产权保护，存在周期长、举证难、维权成本高、赔偿低、效果差等问题。也正是这些原因的存在，导致在现实中，大量侵权行为“民不举官不究”。创新是社会进步的最大力量，对创新的维护是一个社会最大的底线。从这一意义上讲，在涉及知识产权保护问题上，必须采取零容忍态度，就像反腐败一样，要有不计成本、不留死角的精神。 &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">还应该看到，知识产权保护面临着文化土壤问题。在知识侵权案件中，如果说不法分子是元凶的话，那么大量的“吃瓜群众”，则在一定程度上起着“帮凶”的作用。拿《人民的名义》招致泄露来讲，面对种子资源，很多人不仅自己率先尝试，而且在朋友圈里大量分享。如果我们养成知识产权的文化自觉，就会自觉对非法资源说“不”。网上曾经流行一句话，叫做“我们欠周星驰一张票”。在涉及版权问题上，就应该有这样的认识。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">随着《人民的名义》热播，守护“李达康书记的GDP”成了流行词。当前，亟须以“人民的名义”捍卫知识产权，要像守护达康书记一样守护版权。希望这成为一个重要节点，推动知识产权保护春天的到来。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">来源《北京青年报》，作者：乔杉</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2', '10000', '', '0', '1', '');
INSERT INTO `jbr_article_data` VALUES ('160', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月14日青年教师高校科技成果转移转化主题沙龙在国家技术转移中部中心大楼9楼众创咖啡馆举办，来自中国地质大学（武汉）的各学院青年教师代表参加。本次沙龙由中国地质大学（武汉）人事处主办，中国地质大学（武汉）知识产权与技术转移中心、中部知光技术转移有限公司协办。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/d/file/content/2017/04/58fadf13db948.png\" title=\"QQ截图20170422124935.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20170422124935.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国地质大学（武汉）知识产权与技术转移中心副主任罗林波带来题为《最新科技成果转化政策解读及我校技术转移与产业孵化平台介绍》的报告，简单介绍了武汉地质资源环境研究院，以及中国地质大学（武汉）知识产权与技术转移中心工作进展情况。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">罗林波副主任围绕高校知识产权保护热点问题、专利布局与挖掘、专利申请材料的撰写、学校专利申请流程以及教育部科技成果转化相关政策等话题与青年教师们展开讨论与交流。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><br/></p>', '2', '10000', '', '0', '1', '');
INSERT INTO `jbr_article_data` VALUES ('161', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4月9日，武汉马拉松2万余人在雨中火热开跑，场面热烈非凡。 同样火热的三创论坛第7期如约而至，本期主讲人优必选CTO熊友军为我们带来了《服务机器人发展趋势和关键技术》的主题报告，内容精彩纷呈，现场掌声不断。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">本次论坛由国家技术转移中部中心技术转移综合服务市场、中国地质大学（武汉）科学技术发展院、中国地质大学（武汉）自动化学院联合举办。中国地质大学（武汉）科发院副院长刘珩担任主持，来自企业的代表和高校师生近70余人参与论坛。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://test2.jbr.net.cn:820/d/file/content/2017/04/58fadbfc69cf8.jpg\" title=\"1.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"478\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal; width: 640px; height: 478px;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">论坛伊始，熊友军介绍了机器人主要分为工业机器人、特种机器人和服务机器人三类，此外他还对世界先进机器人做了展示，其中美国加州理工的一款应用于医疗领域的机器人，运用肌肉传感技术辅助患者行走，因其性能好、实用性强，且是刚需产品，所以颇受关注。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/d/file/content/2017/04/58fadc68c11d8.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 640px; height: 426px;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">熊友军认为未来服务机器人的研发将是整个行业的方向，并总结了服务机器人发展趋势，在运动控制和人工智能上将无限接近人，服务机器人将成为下一代的消费级的人机交互中心，赢得家庭成员信任最终成为家庭成员，服务机器人的新交互方式将重新定义数据价值颠覆现有的产业生态。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;\">掌握服务机器人关键技术，提高机器人的感知、认知、理解、检测和识别的性能，做人形机器人，并将其商业化、产业化，带领行业步入新台阶，正是目前熊友军和他的团队一直努力的目标。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;\"><img src=\"/d/file/content/2017/04/58fadca87a698.jpg\" title=\"3.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">熊友军精彩的报告，所阐述的前沿科学技术以及研发理念，让人惊叹不已，会场内掌声不断。报告结束后，互动环节里不少老师和专家同熊友军就目前在机器人领域的研究中所遇到的问题进行了交流。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">据悉，熊友军是深圳市优必选科技有限公司CTO、华中科技大学机器人遥操作博士、中国人工智能协会机器人专业委员会会员。登上猴年春晚舞台的明星机器人Alpha 1S（阿尔法一代），就来自优必选。优必选2008年创建，2015年初A轮融资成功估值1亿美元，2016年B轮拿到10亿美元融资，最新估值40亿美元，曾被CB insights评为全球唯一一家服务机器人独角兽公司。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; min-height: 1em; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p>', '2', '10000', '', '0', '1', '');
INSERT INTO `jbr_article_data` VALUES ('162', '<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4月17日</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第15届中国国际人才交流大会在深圳举办，我公司总经理罗林波受邀出席，并在<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">APEC创新协作与大学技术转移研专场讨会上，代表中部高校和运营机构做技术转移报告</span>。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/d/file/content/2017/04/58fada58f3368.jpg\" title=\"1.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"504\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 504px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">研讨会由国家技术转移海峡中心和国际技术转移协作网络（ITTN）承办，邀请到来自澳大利亚、德国、新加坡等14个APEC经济体技术转移方面专家和国内的高校、科研院所共计28位嘉宾。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://test2.jbr.net.cn:820/d/file/content/2017/04/58fada8a750a8.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"504\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; white-space: normal; width: 700px; height: 504px;\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;本次研讨会关注 APEC 区域技术转移人才引进与合作体系建设、协作网络构建，促进 APEC 区域经济体科技创新与国际技术转移交流合作。通过邀请到的不同经济体代表结合自己所在经济体内的知识商品化实践情况进行对比探讨，对既有的参考知识体系补充、拓展，综合形成一个惠及更多经济体、覆盖更多知识商品化实践情况的知识体系。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/d/file/content/2017/04/58fadae6cec98.jpg\" title=\"3.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"502\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 502px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 据悉，2016年国际技术转移协作网络（ITTN）与福建省科技厅国家技术转移海峡中心共同申请了科技部国际合作司“2016年度中国亚太经合组织合作基金”——“APEC 成员经济体国际技术转移人才培养与实践指导计划项目”，承担开展APEC创新协作与大学技术转移研讨会、举办系列培训等工作任务。借第15届中国国际人才交流大会高端平台，ITTN组织本次“APEC创新协作与大学技术转移研讨会”，作为项目重点活动之一。</span></p>', '2', '10000', '', '0', '1', '');
INSERT INTO `jbr_article_data` VALUES ('163', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月6日上午，湖北省知识产权局局长张彦林、副局长程浩, 中国地质大学（武汉）副校长赖旭龙等领导一行到中部知光技术转移有限公司调研知识产权运营工作。公司总经理罗林波、副总经理高珺出席调研会议。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/d/file/content/2017/04/58fabffa2a878.png\" title=\"blob.png\" alt=\"blob.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 500px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">会上，罗林波总经理汇报了公司去年知识产权运营情况，主要介绍了长江经济带高校知识产权运营特色平台的筹备情况，以及湖北省知识产权与创新发展研究院建设进展。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">湖北省知识产权局领导充分肯定了公司知识产权运营工作成效，对下一步知识产权运营平台以及研究院建设提出指导意见。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">省局领导指出，运营平台要突出高校服务特色，积极探索高校知识产权运营有效途径，避免与其他平台同质化竞争，寻求差异化发展；湖北省知识产权与创新发展研究院要定位于应用型发展方向，为湖北省产业发展与政府决策提供参考依据。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">会上，省局领导还就知识产权运营中存在的困难提出了解决意见，鼓励公司员工要克服困难，聚焦业务，再创佳绩。</p><p><br/></p>', '2', '10000', '', '0', '1', '');
INSERT INTO `jbr_article_data` VALUES ('164', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">　3月10日，高校科技成果转化政策研讨及操作实务培训会在中国地质大学(武汉)迎宾楼学术报告厅顺利召开。教育部科技司高新处处长张建华、东湖高新区国家税务局总经济师方波、中国地质大学(武汉)党委副书记朱勤文等领导出席会议，70余家省内外高校和企事业单位嘉宾共计200余人参会。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;\">　　朱勤文介绍了地大概况，学校科技成果转移转化工作在体制机制建设和产业孵化方面的工作思考与探索。她希望地大与各高校同仁一起加强研究与实践，加强高校的科技成果转化工作，区域经济的发展做出应有贡献。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/d/file/content/2017/04/58f9d8f641ac8.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 500px;\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" title=\"1.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\">张建华带来题为《高校科技成果转移转化行动计划》的主题报告。他介绍了国家对创新驱动发展的总体部署，分析了我国高校科技成果存在的问题，结合《教育部 科技部关于加强高等学校科技成果转移转化工作的若干意见》文件精神，详细解读了教育部的指导思路和促进高校科技成果转移转化的新举措。他希望各高校能高度重视，采取切实举措，加快推进科技成果转移转化工作，为把我国建设成为创新型国家和世界科技创新强国做出新的更大贡献。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">　　方波带来《从股权激励看税收对科研成果转化的支持》主题报告，介绍了技术入股(股权激励)、技术转让、大学科技园和科技孵化器三种情况下的税收政策，通过案例详细生动地介绍了科技成果转移转化过程中的企业和个人面临的税收问题。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">　　清华大学成果与知识产权管理办公室副主任张友生、武汉大学科技成果转化办公室副主任赵龙飞、中国地质大学(武汉)知识产权与技术转移中心副主任罗林波分别介绍了三个高校在科技成果转移转化方面做出的思考、探索与实践，在思想转变与政策理解、体制机制设计、管理制度与流程制定、技术入股处置等关键方面进行了经验分享。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal;\">　　本次会议由国家技术转移中部中心技术转移综合服务市场的运营主体(中部知光技术转移有限公司)主办，中国地质大学(武汉)、湖北省高校校办产业协会、湖北省知识产权与创新发展研究院、武汉市技术转移机构联盟、科创知光高校技术转移(武汉)有限公司等单位给予大力支持。</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/d/file/content/2017/04/58f9d8fe425b8.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" title=\"2.jpg\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 500px;\"/></p>', '2', '10000', '', '0', '1', '');
